                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.51A/382: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-08-13T12:00:00+03:25">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 13, 1927—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received August 13—11:42 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>53. Acting under authorization of Department’s 39 [bis], August 9, I have today
                    delivered note to Persian Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Philip</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
